5 Roman'; font-size:11pt">However, if you are not an expert in the Access to Health Records Act, Freedom of Information Act and Data Protectio</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">n Act and gave to learn about such things, your work hours will</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt"> increase on this low estimate.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">This complexity makes it almost impossible for you to avoid employing a lawyer.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">Clever compo-seekers will have gone this route from the start.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">The </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">Health Board hopes that you can't afford one.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">Because you are grieving, nice and still trying to understand what went wrong and don't want to sue anyone...</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11p