<p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">But</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt"> will believe the chief </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">nursing officer as he/she hasn't a clue as to what to do otherwise and has to write lots of reports on 'Care and Dignity'</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt"> and about how well the board is doing. And, in particular, the CEO.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">Then rush off to reorganise ... Well...everything.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">This is a </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">permanent state. Until the next chief executive arrives to reorganise again and write more reports snappily entitled</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt"> 'Dignity and Care'.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">CEO correspondence is</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span><span style="font-famil