rutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">:::::</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">The Ombu</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">dsman</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">1. The complaint handler/ caseworker, whose intelligence can range from the level of a dim - but arrogant - call centre operative, who likes to shout a bit at callers, to that of a reasonably understanding person.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">How your</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt"> case goes will depend </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">entirely on your luck in the caseworker draw and not how just it is.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">Complainants are advised to repeat the same thing (as in parrot training)</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt"> in the hope that the exact nature if the complaint can be repeated by caseworker to the clinical advisor </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">....even though actual understanding of content might be absent.<