utiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt"> sadly bereaved, becoming enraged and now simply flabbergasted -</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt"> do not take this final rejection slip personally.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">What were the chances? You would have only</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt"> been in a marginally better position if you had posted yo</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">ur complaint down a drain.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">However, for eternal optimists who simply must:</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">1. The caseworker who 'reads' your complaint.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt"> This person may not get:</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">*</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt"> your name right</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">*</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt"> the correct legal Act/s involved</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">*</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt"> or, most shockingly, what you are </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">complaining about.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">Despite being hampered by this creative lack of concentration, the caseworker is entrusted with a large rubber stamp....which reads 'W'.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">( For Wastepaper bin,</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt"> of course..shame on those that thought anything else).</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">The </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">caseworker can happily consign your case to the bin for a reason that you cannot possibly comprehend.... as it is astonishingly one that you haven't complained about. Simply because the Ombudsman's decision is final.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">You will hope to get a letter which e</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">xplains why your case was rejected.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">Hope on.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">The PHSO does not have to explain its reasoning to a mere prole like you.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">If it did, you might be able to ask why it peremptorily dismissed your case, as, if an explanation was given,</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt"> it may seem that you</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">r case</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt"> had been inadvertently mixed up with someone else's and the explanation made no sense.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">So you may never know...Unless if course, you are prepared to start all over again on the ultra-masochistic Freedom of Information/Data Protection request pa</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">per trail.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">Reread strategies to 'withhold information'</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt"> and 'dismissal of anyone who is chippy enough to ask about our private government business' tactics above ).</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">Don't be dispirited that the old ploy of</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt"> simply not answering your question ....but an</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">swering the one they'd wished you'd asked...</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt"> is used. Yet again.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">There are some fine examples of this on the 'What Do They Know'</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">website if you are in the mood for laughing and groaning simultaneously. Removal of tight garments is advised for your own </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">protection.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">Nb. * Don't forget to ask for handwritten notes. The PHSO forgets to include them.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">Q.</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">How many of the letters that are addressed specifically to Dame</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">Julie Mellor, does she read herself?</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">A As we receive a great many enquiries each </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">year (in 2012/13, we received 26,961), it would not be possible to extract this information for you without exceeding the appropriate limit as set out at section 12 of the Freedom of Information Act 2000.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">This example, now used as compulsory training f</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">or all would-be complainants:</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><a href="https://www.whatdotheyknow.com/request/dame_julie_mellor#incoming-433572"><span style="color:#0000ff; font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt; text-decoration:underline">https://www.whatdotheyknow.com/request/dame_julie_mellor#incoming-433572</span></a></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">2. The Review Team</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">As the Review team just </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">sign stuff off and don't</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt"> bother to read the files and so are simply unaware if what you complained about ... let alone understand it, it is a complete waste of time appealing to it.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">Nb</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">Don't bother complaining about any member of this team, as your comp</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">laint goes</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt"> back to ....and is run by: (You've guessed it..) The Review Team.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">The P</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">HSO has no ethics officer as it</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">s staff are all trusted to get everything at least 100 percent , which, if course is better than the</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">98.6 percent that the previous Ombudsma</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">n was able to achieve.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">3. The Ombudsman</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">This semi-mythical creature, is hardly ever sighted</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt"> by complainants and exists only in places of power.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">It is no use appealing to her office for sense, as bereaved complainants might be savagely put in </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">their place by a braying henchwoman.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">Nb. It is more difficult to be informed the Ombudsman's timetable than it is to get the HRH, Her Majesty the Queen's.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">In fact, it is rumoured that, statistically,</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt"> a bereaved complainant might as well write to the Q</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">ueen as they would be more likely to get a signed invite to a garden party, at Buckingham Palace, than a meeting with the Ombudsman.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt"> (* MP's note: This means you too).</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">Time taken:</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt"> About four years</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">Paper pile:</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt"> Leaning Tower of Pisa standard.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">E</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">nd result:</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">*</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt"> Refurbishment of hospital ward. Now the dying have single</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt"> rooms to die in and</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt"> the nursing standards seem to be a lot higher.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">* Private companies are still able to write exactly what they like about people on NHS files - even though they may not even be the patient </span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">- if the complainant chooses the Ombudsman route.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">People may not know:</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">*who is writing about them</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">*why they </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">have written it</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">* or what it says.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">The 'public interest'</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt"> argument is not even worth being considered by the PHSO as one which overrides the secrecy</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt"> of private companies -</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt"> which may wish to withhold crucial files to protect the NHS,</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt"> and even retain </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">their lucrative contracts on the basis of doing so - even in proven Ombudsman- upheld negligence cases.</span></p><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 55 Roman'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span><